# ORIG TITLE    Basketball: Gasol Out . 
# ORIG CONTENT  Lakers forward Pau Gasol will not be representing Spain in EuroBasket 2013. This announcement comes less than a week after undergoing surgery on his knee to eliminate scar tissue. Gasol is expected to fully recover from the procedure and return to his NBA squad next season. Pau Gasol is a key player of the Spanish basketball team, with whom he was European champion in 2011 and Olympic silver medalist in 2012. 
